text: former railway station in St Helier forms part of Liberty Wharf. Liberty Wharf is a shopping centre in St Helier, Jersey, which opened in November 2010. Much of the site is a former abattoir which was restored and converted for use as a shopping centre. ==References== ==External links== *Liberty Wharf Shopping Centre Category:Buildings and structures in Saint Helier Category:Shopping centres in Jersey
